“The galaxy isn’t as far away as you think!”

“Looking to get far far away? Let us help plan your next trip to another galaxy!”

View Destination by:
    
    Terrain/Climate
        Choose terrain/climate category from list
        Choose planet from list in that category
            Show starting cost to travel to planet
            Show POI’s & wildlife on selected planet
        Plan trip
            Choose lodging
            Choose rental transportation
            Choose transportation to planet
    
    POI’s
        Choose POI from list
            Planet will automatically be selected based on chosen POI
            Show other available POI’s on same planet
            Show climate/terrain and wildlife for planet
            Show starting cost to travel to planet
        Plan trip
            Choose lodging
            Choose rental transportation
            Choose transportation to planet
    
    Wildlife
        Choose Wildlife from list
            Show list of planets with selected wildlife
            Select desired planet
                Show climate/terrain for planet
                Show available POI’s planet
                Show starting cost to travel to planet
        Plan trip
            Choose lodging
            Choose rental transportation
            Choose transportation to planet
